===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|talken}}, {{m|enm|talkien}}, from {{inh|en|ang|*tealcian|t=to talk, chat}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*talkōną|t=to talk, chatter}}, frequentative form of {{der|en|gem-pro|*talōną|t=to count, recount, tell}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*dol-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*del-|t=to aim, calculate, adjust, count}}, equivalent to {{af|en|tell|-k|nocat=1}}. Cognate with {{cog|sco|talk||to talk}}, {{cog|nds|taalken||to talk}}. Related also to {{cog|da|tale||to talk, speak}}, {{cog|sv|tala||to talk, speak, say, chatter}}, {{cog|is|tala||to talk}}, {{cog|ang|talian||to count, calculate, reckon, account, consider, think, esteem, value; argue; tell, relate; impute, assign}}. More at {{l|en|tale}}.

